AUDIO: 'behind and sneak up on them. So, of course, you can write the prompt on your own, but I like to use Chat GPT for it because it can give you a detailed seedance 2.0 prompt. So, the first thing that I like to do is just take a'

[04:20] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'screenshot anywhere in the video. So, I can do this in Premiere Pro just by exporting the frame here. And then what I can do is I can just upload the screenshot so Chat GPT gets an idea of what\'s happening in the'

